import * as React from 'react';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';
import {Box, Grid, Item, Paper} from '@mui/material';


const HomeScreen = () => {
        <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
            <Grid item xs={8}>
                <Item>xs=8</Item>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Item>xs=4</Item>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Item>xs=4</Item>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={8}>
                <Item>xs=8</Item>
            </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Box>
}

export default HomeScreen
